com.ihealth.communication.control

Interface UpgradeProfile


  • public interface UpgradeProfile
    Public APIs for the Upgrade serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager.registerClientCallback(com.ihealth.communication.manager.iHealthDevicesCallback) register. When new data from Upgrade device, The Callback{#iHealthDevicesCallback #onDeviceNotify} can be triggered should call.
